# Deploying Punga

1. Copy the following files into the directory of your choice:

    punga.py
    parable.py
    bootstrap.parable

2. Setup a symlink to punga:

    ln -s punga.py punga.cgi

3. Create an .htaccess:

    AddHandler cgi-script .cgi
    Options FollowSymLinks +ExecCGI
    DirectoryIndex punga.cgi

4. Set punga.cgi as executable:

    chmod +x punga.cgi

